Blurb:: Generate a D-optimal sampling design

Description::
This option will generate a sampling design that is approximately
D-optimal by downselecting from a set of candidate sample points.

<b> Default Behavior </b>

If not specified, a standard sampling design (MC or LHS) will be generated.

Topics::	
Examples::
\verbatim
method
  sampling
    sample_type random
    samples = 20
    d_optimal
\endverbatim
